SCHEMA: interaction/tool_tag.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.interaction.tool_tag
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define tool compatibility tags used by ActionSurface affordance filtering.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record tool_tag
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - tool_tag_id: id
    - description: string
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- Tool tags are semantic compatibility labels only.
- Tool tag matching cannot mutate authoritative state.
